// Thread 1: Computing indices 4 to 7
// Thread 2: Computing indices 8 to 11
// Thread 3: Computing indices 12 to 15
// Thread 0: Local sum = 10
// Thread 1: Local sum = 26
// Thread 2: Local sum = 42
// Thread 3: Local sum = 58
//
// ==================================================
